description: Does Jon have what it takes to find the truth? Can Jake push him to do the unmentionable? And what lies southward, in the sand and beneath the sun?
name: Are You Listening?

description:
“AGE OF X: AFTERMATH!”

The X-Men have escaped the AGE OF X and returned to Utopia…unaware that something sinister followed them back. Upon discovering that this new evil has been loosed into the world, Rogue and Magneto round up a team of X-Men to hunt it down. But is this motley new crew of X-Men prepared for what awaits them?

A bonus feature includes Rogue helping the X-Men track down their missing comrades Havok and Polaris in deep space.

This issue also includes a reprinting of New Mutants #27, the first meeting between Charles Xavier and his son, Legion!

Some characters listed here only appear in flashbacks, such as Chamber appearing in Revenant's memories.
name: Lost Legions, Part 1; Flashback; Into the Abyss

description:
In this issue:

"La Vendetta di Ra" (conclusion)

"Operazione Arca"
name: Operazione Arca

description:
The biggest Star Wars event of 2011--LucasArts and BioWare’s Star Wars: The Old Republic online game--gets a fresh, new story set concurrent with the game, written by one of its senior writers!

The Lost Suns stands alone as an accessible Star Warsadventure, introducing a new hero with a new mission! It also intertwines with the narrative of the game, revealing secrets players will find nowhere else! Theron Shan--descendant of the legendary bloodline that includes Jedi Bastila Shan and Satele Shan--is no Jedi he’s a Republic spy! His mission: to discover the blackest secret at the heart of the evil Sith Empire!

The first issue in a brand-new story!

Written by Alexander Freed, a senior writer of the game!

Readers who are familiar with The Old Republic game will be able to make connections directly from the game to this comic story line!
name: Part 1 of 5

volume.name: Star Wars: The Old Republic - The Lost Suns

description: Dylan and Groucho save a man from the aggression of some thugs . Signs are that this is a bum , but in reality the man is tormented by the death of his wife and daughter , killed years earlier by a strange ritual , and that's is why he's living on the street a few meters from his house . A few days later a professor of mathematics and Satan worshiper begins to kill his students ...
name: La porta dell'inferno

description: A small specimen of homo habilis , a species extinct  two million years ago, is hit by a bus in central London . Dr. Pelham , who attended the scene , contacts the i nvestigator of nightmare . Strange prehistoric animals begin to appear, quietly walking in the streets of the City . Dylan investigates and discovers that all converge on one point : the old Docks .
name: Fratelli di un altro tempo

description: Greg Fenton , divorced college professor with a passion for exotic plants , dies dehydrated before the house of the investigator of nightmare , poisoned by a toxic substance of unknown origin . Dylan , while investigating the mysterious death, is in turn infected and has only twenty-four hours of life ...
name: I demoni

description: London plunges into an endless night , where dreams become reality and reality does not exist. Dylan finds himself to be the only person wide awake in a  London fallen asleep because of  superficiality and indifference .
name: Notte senza fine

description: London is invaded by an incredible number of rats, able to feed on human flesh . The emergency also means that the army will intervene, but Dylan has to find out where the rats of this horrendous invasion come from.
name: L'orrenda invasione

description: Even machines have a soul . This is the answer given by Timothy Brynard to the many accidents that happen in London . That's right : the cars drive themselves to cause accidents and kill their passengers to take revenge for being treated as objects .
name: La rivolta delle macchine

description: What happens if our memory is erased ? That's what happens to Dylan , whose death has been erased from his memory. Could he continue to live as it were never happened ?
name: Il guardiano della memoria

description: From the pages of the red-hot Vertigo series comes a five-issue spinoff miniseries! It's World War II in Nazi-occupied Romania as vampire hunters Felicia Book and Cash McCogan (last seen in the critically acclaimed AMERICAN VAMPIRE story "Devil in the Sand") go behind enemy lines with the secret organization known as the Vassals of the Morningstar in search of a rumored vampire cure. But their haunted, twisted past with Skinner Sweet makes the mission more difficult than they imagined. Superstar artist Sean Murphy (JOE THE BARBARIAN) joins Scott Snyder to tell a story of horror and history, expanding the American Vampire mythology in a way that changes this story forever.
name: Part One

first_appearance_teams.name: The Vassals of the Morning Star

team_credits.name: The Vassals of the Morning Star

volume.name: American Vampire: Survival of the Fittest

description: Ken Harrell , a former friend of Dylan , kills his wife and is confined in a psychiatric clinic . After two years manages to escape and wants to take revenge on Dylan Dog .
name: Il volo dello struzzo

description: Doc and his team chase the mysterious blonde to Russia, where dead things seem to be coming back to life – including a giant, airplane-hating pterodactyl! Can Doc outfly the outdated beast in his jetpack and save the girl? It seems everyone is dying to get their hands on the Apis Bull – but what exactly will it unlock?
name: Raise the Khan Chapter Three: Ring of Iron

description:
As the Tattooed Man battles Vixen, Deathstroke and The Titans finally put aside their differences to escape the telepathic madman Drago. And if they do manage to meet up with Osiris and his sister Isis, will they be able to survive the long-awaited confrontation with the JLA?

Continued in Titans Annual #1
name: Broken Promises, Part 4: No Way Out

description:
The start of a new story arc! A body has washed up in Metropolis, and it looks like Batman's the killer! Superman knows better, but Clark Kent gets assigned to go to Gotham to investigate. And that's when things start to get freaky...

Summary

Some time ago in Metropolis, Jimmy Olsen is trying to impress a model and while taking her picture he finds the dead body of Garrett Remington, a reporter for the Gotham Gazette and one of Perry White's friends. Perry sends Clark Kent to report on what happened to Garrett and to see if th fact that Garrett was working on a story about who Batman really is under the mask.

Clark takes th next train to Gotham City and meets up with Batman. the two have a brief stand off about what being a hero needs to be, and Batman storms off to investagate the Batman way.

Batman breaks into Garrett apartment and finds out that the report had put it together that Batman is Bruce Wayne. He destroys the evidence, but not before being spotted by the police.

Mean while Clark tries to solve the murder the reporter way, by talking to Martin Mayne the editor in chief of the Gotham Gazette. he discoves that it was true that Garrett may have figured out who Batman really is, but hasn't told anyone and kept his notes under lock and key. Martin and Clark are interupted when the police radio in Martin's office reports that Batman set off a bomb.

Seconds later Superman arrives at the scene and speaks to Comm. Gordon who believes Batman is innocent in Garrett's death but still thinks its too much for Batman to handle on his own.

After escaping the Gotham police Batman meets back up with Superman and learns that the evidence that Garrett found was a serial number on one of Batman's tools that her mistakenly left behind. The serial number linked it back to Wayne tech and Bruce Wayne.

The last scene Batman leaves Superman standing on a roof top saying "I told you i don't need your help"
name: The Secret, Part 1 of 3

description:
Booster knows that the Flashpoint world isn't his own. But how does he get back? How does he make things right?

After rescuing a woman during his battle against Doomsday, Booster gets the shock of a lifetime when he discovers the monster is controlled by Nathaniel Adam aslo known as Captain Atom. He also uses his computer skills to determine the changes to this new reality and how they came to pass. He's on the trail for clues regarding the chronal changes when he's suddenly and savagely attacked again by Doosmday.
name: Turbulence, Part Two

description:
FLASH FACT! They can't survive unless they find their maker!  

Frankenstein and the Creatures of The Unknown uncovers the wierd war tales of the FLASHPOINT world. When Frankenstein awakens in issue one, his first words are “was… something… left… undone?” What is he referring to? Where has Frankenstein been?
name: Part 1: Weird War Tales!

volume.name: Flashpoint: Frankenstein and the Creatures of the Unknown

description:
FLASH FACT! He will stop at nothing to find his lost treasure!

Deathstroke and his crew aboard the Ravager continue the search for his missing daughter Rose. After enlisting new crew members following a battle against his rival The Warlord, Deathstroke comes face to face with Emperor Aquaman and his brother Ocean Master!
name: Separation Anxiety

volume.name: Flashpoint: Deathstroke and the Curse of the Ravager

description:
FLASH FACT! He loves someone he should not!

He is the biggest hero in Central City. His fans adore him. Women want to be with him. But Citizen Cold's past is catching up with him, and its only a matter of time before his dream life of fame and wealth is going to come to a screeching halt. But that doesn't mean he's going down without a fight.
name: Cold Hearted, Chapter 1

description:
FLASH FACT! He will drown the world – then rule it! 
 
Once set to enter a political marriage with Princess Diana of the Amazons, Emperor Aquaman now seeks revenge on the Amazons for the death of his true queen, Mera. Forging an alliance with Markovia, Aquman abducts the country's king, Geo-Force, and uses his powers within a giant seismic bomb, leading to war, and the flooding of half of Europe.
name: Part One

description:
Amid the protests of both human rights groups and Bruce Wayne, a new Arkham rises. The Joker is scheduled to be its first inmate, but not if Harley Quinn has anything to say about it. Meanwhile, Batman's suspicions lead him to investigate just who is really behind this new, more sprawling asylum and what their motivations might be.

Batman investigates the new Mayor of Gotham only to encounter the real power behind Arkham City, Hugo Strange. Meanwhile, Harley Quinn rescues the Joker from his murderous jailers.
name: Breaking Ground

description: To survive the Assassination Tournament, Red Robin must survive an attack from Scarab's Covenant of Ka, make it to Russia in time to rescue a critically injured oligarch, track the mercenary Promise and come to an unexpected confrontation with the mysterious sister of Ra's al Ghul!
name: 7 Days of Death, Part Two: It's Not Parandia...

description: Things get ugly as The Birds of Prey are trapped in a cunning puzzle box of a skyscraper, pursued by a nightmarish killer who holds all the cards, leaving only the Huntress, the reluctant aide of Renee Montoya, The Question to free them! And what effect does the death of Oracle have on the team as they race to escape from hell?
name: Hostile Takeover, Part Two of Two: No Sentence Shall Be Commuted

description: The Red Hood is out! But the bigger mystery is who broke him out of prison – and why? His liberators seem to have plans for him. Plans that Jason wants no part of. It's a street brawl, and unlikely allies come together! Batman, Robin and The Red Hood must fight alongside one another in a knockdown, drag-out battle, taking on the people who sprung Jason Todd.
name: The Streets Run Red, Part 2 of 3: Exit Strategy
The Vessel with the Pestle

description:
The truth of the Avengers and their never-been-told-before origins have been revealed, but how will Nick Fury's shocking past save the life of an Avenger who's life hangs in the balance?

One Avenger will be changed forever. Will they live or will they die?? And who is the new face of H.A.M.M.E.R.?!
name: Infinity, part 5

description:
The badass, broom-swinging vigilante Maidman, the “cross-dressing crusader,” is interviewed by the super-phony “celebricape” TV host of an ill-fated talk show. The confab soon degenerates from happy chatter to cape-on-cape violence! Meanwhile, costumed crimefighter Empowered exploits Maidman's fearsome reputation not only to victimize hapless supervillains, but also to get the upper hand on her recalcitrant boyfriend!

In a new one-shot spinning off from the sexy superhero comedy graphic-novel series  Empowered, creator Adam Warren draws fourteen black-and-white pages that frame and cruelly interrupt a fifteen-page story painted in glorious full color by special guest artist Emily “No Relation” Warren!
name: Ten Questions for the Maidman

description:
Tennis is Mill Collins whole life...but as the lowest ranking student at the Wayde Tennis Academy, she's about to lose her scholarship, and any chance at reaching her dream. Her coach has given up on her, her aunt thinks she doesn't try, and the only one who believes in her is a washed-up drunk...how wrong can things possible go before Mill catches a break?

Cover Price: US $4.99

Format: Color; Standard Comic Issue; 48 pages
name: Book 1

description: Continuing the sequel to the smash hit 1990 film, Douglas Quaid and his dream lady Melina find themselves reeling after the tragic conclusion to issue #1. Yet there is no time to mourn as the Mars colony struggles to keep itself from falling apart. With more tragedy on the way, Quaid and Melina have to figure out what's going on before all hell breaks loose. Meanwhile the mystery of Mars itself deepens, and as our heroes discover, the creation of air for Mars was just the beginning.

First, Wolverine was sent to hell. Then he was forced to fight for control of his own mind against demonic invaders. All thanks to the machinations of a mysterious group called the Red Right Hand. Who are they and what is their grudge against Logan? And how do they hope to survive now that Wolverine has come looking for some revenge of his own?

Mexico- Wolverine has found the secret hide out of The Red Right Hand, and once inside he is jumped by Cannonfoot. Wolverine makes quick work of Cannonfoot and is jumped by Shadow Stalker.

Meanwhile the leader of The Red Right Hand recounts how Wolverine killed his father and how he spent his life trying to get revenge. He has tried to kill Wolverine directly but realized he couldn't do it alone so he started The Red Right Hand.
name: Wolverine's Revenge, Part 1

description: TWO AWESOME STORIES IN ONE COSMIC BOOK! This is it: the galaxy's most powerful squad and most beloved duo face their fiery finales! First, the Annihilators must prove they are the ace team of universal protectors that Star-Lord dreamed they could be...or perish in the attempt! Meanwhile, Rocket Raccoon and Groot face the horrible, reality-twisting menace – who has a key connection to Rocket's secret past – that lurks in the heart of the Half-World Asylum! Want to show the House of Ideas that you want more Marvel Cosmic? Spread the word and buy this issue!

concept_credits.name: Rocket Raccoon & Groot Themed Variant Cover

first_appearance_concepts.name: Rocket Raccoon & Groot Themed Variant Cover

description: Finally, Jim comes face-to-face with someone from his past—an important family member. However, with the revelation comes a deadly surprise
name: Q&A - Part 2

description: Before Captain America, before The Twelve, there was The Aviatrix, The Operative, Achilles, The Revenant and The Surgeon! What drives these five heroes to pull on masks and take to the rooftops of Manhattan? What dark conspiracy not only brings them together, but threatens to tear the America apart? On the hunt to solve a brutal murder, our champions will smash their way from gleaming penthouses of privilege to squalid alleyways, as the full horror of their enemies’ schemes unfolds!

Before the caped crusader patrolled the streets, before horn head prowled the back alleys, the original dark avenger hunted evil men. The Black Bat is back, and hell’s coming with him!

*A “Return of the Originals” event!

All new stories!

DA Anthony Quinn is sick of watching criminals slip through his fingers due to legal technicalities. When a mobster’s attempt to destroy evidence goes horribly wrong, Quinn finds himself blinded by acid and hopelessly broken. Now sightless, Quinn sharpens his other four senses to near superhuman levels and develops a sixth ‘radar’ sense. He vows to work outside the law to do whatever it takes to bring criminals to justice. Plus: Death Angel, the avenging hand of justice. The critically acclaimed new pulp character co-stars in this gritty, noir battle of good versus evil on the mean streets and in the darkest recesses of the human mind.
name: Return of the Originals

description: From SAVAGE to SENSATIONAL! With John Byrne at the helm, witness She-Hulk go where no super hero has gone before: right through the fourth wall! Vs. Spider-Man! Beheaded! Against the wrath of Dr. Bong! Alongside Santa Claus! On her own Star Truck! Hosting a Golden Age guest star! Featuring the Wasp, Mr. Fantastic and Razorback! Collecting SENSATIONAL SHE-HULK #1-8 and material from MARVEL COMICS PRESENTS (1988) #18.
name: Volume One

description: The true origin of Thor's archenemy and Marvel's most unpredictable villain! He is the lie-smith; he is the shape-changer; he is the fire that burns. The God of Mischief and Trickery, Loki. Meet the mirthful, beloved young man that made all the Asgardians laugh...until the first time he killed. Discover the gnarled roots of his twisted, unrelenting hatred of the Asgardians. And learn the chilling truth of why he'll never be stopped...Collects Loki (2010) #1-4.
name: HC/TPB

description: When Hope Summers returned from the future, she triggered the rebirth of the mutant gene. Five lights appeared on Cerebra, and five mutants' powers came to life -- but their activations have been chaotic and dangerous, nearly killing each of them. With Rogue and the four of the five new mutants, Hope heads to Japan to join Cyclops, Wolverine and the fifth light. But will this new light be a hero or a villain?
name: TPB

volume.name: Generation Hope: The Future's A Four-Letter Word

description: Marvel's merry mutants are coming at you again with another massive Omnibus! It's the original X-Men-Cyclops, Beast, Angel, Iceman and Marvel Girl-in their first adventures as Professor X's mutant teen team supreme. Featuring page after page of X-Men milestones-from the team's new costumes, to the death of Professor X, and the first appearances of Havok, Polaris and Sunfire, this volume chronicles a turbulent era for mutantdom. But for every problem there is a solution: Enter Roy Thomas and Neal Adams, and True Believer, you had better grab onto your hat and get ready for one of the most amazing evolutions in Marvel history! These two titanic talents threw caution to the wind with sensational stories that brought the X-Men in sync with the thriving youth culture of the late '60s. Adams' lavish and dynamic visuals merged with Thomas' challenging and contemporary stories to create a comic book series that throbbed with the pulse of the times like none other. Featuring bonuses galore, not to mention the original letters pages, this collection is one for the ages, so reserve your copy today, True Believer! Collecting X-MEN #32-66, AVENGERS #66, KA-ZAR #2-3, MARVEL TALES #30 and NOT BRAND ECHH #4 & #8.
name: Volume Two

first_appearance_locations.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

location_credits.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

description:
Enter the U-Men! When envious humans begin dissecting mutants and grafting their body parts, it's up to the X-Men to stop them! But things at home aren't much better as Cyclops and Jean Grey can't stop fighting, Jean's powers flare out of control, and Professor X's mind is trapped in the body of his comatose evil twin! Introducing the new Angel - and the X-Men have never seen anything like her!

Collecting : NEW X-MEN #118-121.
name: Book 2

description: Panther + Storm + Kraven the Hunter = “Storm Hunter” Parts 1 & 2! From the rooftops to the subway tunnels, why is Spider-Man’s deadly foe stalking T’Challa across the city…and how long until the prey targets the pursuer? Plus: will the world’s greatest predators have anywhere to hide when Ororo arrives and rips the skies open? It’s the first meeting of husband and wife since the Panther’s new status.
name: Storm Hunter Part One

volume.name: Black Panther: The Man Without Fear

description: Fear Itself tie-in! The biggest event of the year continues as 'Fear Itself' tears New York City apart under the Serpent's influence. Spider-Man's right in the middle of it, protecting everyday people... from themselves. But two days in, there's no sign of hope, no sign of salvation, and Spider-Man finds himself at the mercy of a foe even he fears...Vermin.
name: Day Two

description: "Planet Hulk" and "World War Hulk" writer Greg Pak ends his legendary "Incredible Hulk" run -- and he's taking the Green Goliath down with him! To protect his beloved family, Bruce Banner has spent the last year sacrificing himself in titanic clashes with monsters, demons, and the gods themselves. But what happens when the furious monster inside Bruce Banner says enough? Every wish comes true -- and every curse is unleashed -- as the angriest, strongest one there is finally seizes what HE wants. The Hulk's greatest love, most powerful villains, and ultimate triumph converge... in what just might be the end of the Incredible Hulk.
name: Heart of the Monster Part One

description: The untold origin of the Punisher continues. Once upon a time, Frank Castle was just a regular guy, with a steady job and a loving family. A guy just trying to stay out of trouble and make his way. But Nick Fury had other ideas...
name: Frank, Part 3

description: A gang of drug dealers from Mars to Earth hides the goods within the body of the couriers . One of them, a girl from the Colony , carries with her a deadly and highly contagious virus that could cause carnage in the populous cities on Earth. None at the moment is reflecting on the fact that this virus represents a primitive form of life on Mars .
name: Contagio

description: Spider-Man has been wounded and hangs to life by the thinnest of threads. And when the Sinister Six comes for him in his hometown, Spider-Man will truly be in for the fight of his life! Prepare for a rumble in Queens like you've never seen before.
name: Death of Spider-Man: Part 4 of 5

description: Uh-oh…looks like Deadpool made a slight miscalculation. Sure, he wants to die—but he doesn’t want to take down thousands of innocent people with him! It was almost impossible for Deadpool to convince Hulk to come after him—how the hell is he supposed to convince him to stop?
name: Operation: Annihilation Part Two: Clear and Present Anger

description: Spotlighting Marvel’s next movie star: Captain America! When the Super-Soldier investigates a stolen shipment of plutonium, did he ever think it would lead to battling against hordes of genetically re-created species and cavemen? The shield-slinging living legend is now in the fight for his life, and he may be the next one to go...extinct!
name: Back In Time

description: A bizarre story : a cartoon hero is responsible of some heinous crimes . It is a tribute to artist - writer Leone Cimpellin and to the world of comics in general , but it is also an occasion to reiterate the philosophy of the authors of Nathan Never : no story is new , It's always a reworking of something that has already been written .
name: Il vendicatore mascherato

description: Everything you've ever wanted to know about the cast of The Walking Dead. The Survivor's Guide is a handy checklist of all the characters who have appeared in the series thus far, alive or dead. This series is a can't-miss supplement to the hit comic book series that is now a hit TV series on AMC!
name: H to N

description:
During an attempt to steal an old picture protected by Nathan , April and May , the girl's father , Donald Frayn , loses his life, and their sister July is injured. Later, Nathan is invited to dinner by a friend, Anthony Russo, a student, but when he comes to Anthony's home, he finds him dead. Through Anthony 's girlfriend, Saki, Nathan discovers that one of the professors of the boy, Marcus Modens , has compromised the computer of the student... furthermore, it's revealed the reason why in Nathan's future the use of paper (and books) has been abolished.
This issue has been also published in english by Dark Horse Comics in 1999.
name: La biblioteca di Babele

description: Mind-controlling mastermind Maxwell Lord is targeting the members of the defunct Justice League International in this hardcover collecting the first 12 issues of the twice-monthly series tying into BRIGHTEST DAY. Now, surviving members Booster Gold, Captain Atom, Fire and Ice must stop him from destroying the entire Super Hero community.
name: Vol. 1

description: With the Power of Three torn asunder, Phoebe and Paige work to bring their family back together. But a tragically ill-advised plan pulls The Charmed Ones further apart and could leave one of the sisters lost forever.
name: Three Little Wiccans

description: Jolly Jumper falls in love and Lucky Luke has to bring him to Canada.
name: La Belle Province

description: To Government decides to apply the death penalty to the prisoners with the longest sentences, the Daltons among them, to resolve overpopulation in the penitentiaries. Ma Dalton has the idea to marry them, because the law doesn't apply to married prisoners. The Daltons plan to marry the four daughters of an Indian chief.
name: La Corde au Cou

description:
Republican candidate Rutherford B. Hayes is campaigning for the elections, but another republican called Perry Camby proclaimed himself as the official candidate and wants to get rid of Hayes. Lucky Luke has to protect candidate Hayes. 
 
In this issue there are caricatures of George W. Bush, Dick Cheney, Sarah Palin and others.
name: L'Homme de Washington

description: At the time when Abraham Lincoln was president, Lucky Luke has to face a detective called Pinkerton, who has arrested many criminals and considers himself the successor of Lucky Luke.
name: Lucky Luke contre Pinkerton

description: The race for the colonization of the oceans leads a multinational to try a bold experiment : the transformation of a prejudiced criminal in a dangerous amphibious cyborg . He , however , leading a band of pirates, rebels against its creators . It's up to Nathan and his companions to neutralize the bandits . But the technology used to create the cyborg belongs to this world ?
name: I predatori dei mari

description: More classics! More fun! First off, the much requested, first-time-printed in the U.S. 1970 Carl Barks story—recently redrawn by Jippes in the Barks style—“Whale of A Good Deed,” where Scrooge tries to extract some free oil, but his nephews, the Junior Woodchucks, show him the error of his ways! Then enjoy the hilarity as Donald Duck shows just how hard chopping down a tree can be in the William Van Horn backup “Tree's a Crowd,” not having seen print in over a decade!
name: Whale of A Good Deed, Tree's a Crowd

description: For the first time in hardcover, this title collects the story of Jesse Custer's ultimate battle with the Saint of Killers and the forces of Starr — and the catastrophic outcome — originally presented in PREACHER #34-40. Also included: the PREACHER SPECIAL: ONE MAN'S WAR, PREACHER SPECIAL: THE STORY OF YOU-KNOW-WHO and PREACHER SPECIAL: THE GOOD OLD BOYS, starring Starr, Arseface, and Jody and T.C., the evil bastards of Angelville who haunted the Preacher's childhood.
name: Book Four

description: T he mind of a rememberer contains a list of high society names, all members of a Golf Club and colluding with the Mafia. Someone is determined to do anything , even kill , to get rid of the man , but he's under protection by the Alfa Agency, that  is working with the central attorney Office . Nathan stands a romantic complication : the prosecutor investigating officer is Sarah McBain , the woman with whom Nathan  betrayed his wife years before .
name: Bersaglio umano

description: Holed up in an abandoned prison , the men of Alfa and the police must protect the rememberer from ruthless criminals equipped with invisible suits . The game is hard and ruthless , and it will prove more complicated than in appearance , with unexpected twists .
name: Partita mortale

description: Someone is murdering the most important contemporary artists,  " composing " with their corpses artworks  of the past . At the same time a bizarre   cartoon-like hacker , threatens to destroy the entire Metropolitan Museum . A rt is the focus of these two surveys , only apparently unrelated to each other .
name: Bauhaus killer

description: Fist fight!

The election of Franz Hoenzoller for mayor of the City has made ​​critical the already difficult relations between the " homini sapiens " and the mutates . To make matters worse , a dangerous group of extremists planned a massacre of innocent people to blow up an armed conflict between the two races. To avert the threat Nathan will again venture into the hell of the First Level, where he will meet some old friends and enemies .
name: Caccia all'uomo

description: This is the cross-over fans have been clamoring for! It's Starborn and Soldier Zero fighting the vanguard of the Pride with the survival of the galaxy hanging in the balance. Superman's Chris Roberson and Spider-Man's Khary Randolph bring you a Stan Lee superhero clash of the titans like no other! Worlds collide in this epic new issue from Stan 'The Man' Lee! Covers by Dimitri Armand and Matteo Scalera.

A famous olomovies script writer suffers an attack that left her dying . Her security is now entrusted to Nathan , who was a childhood friend of hers . Can the past  come back, after twenty years ? And what is the reason for the attempted murder ? The story is played on continuous flashback that shed light on some episodes of  Nathan adolescence .
name: La storia di Kathy Teller

description: The Army has transformed a man into a super speedy killing machine. W hen he rebels they decide to "erase" him, but the task will not be easy . Alfa Agency is involved in research , bringing to light the corruption that lurks in the military, until the discovery of a prohibited weapon even more terrifying and deadly than the " Lone Runner " .
name: Thor 14

description: They are taking over... From the innovative mind of acclaimed movie producer Gale Anne Hurd, and written by superstar writer and visionary Scott Lobdell, comes this summer's biggest blockbuster new series-The Scourge! With the gargoyle-like infestation reaching further throughout the streets of New York City, Griffin is a man against time as he races to save the city from total annihilation. But, what can one man do against a virtual army of blood thirsty, highly invulnerable, fang-baring creatures?? The shocking answers are right here as The Scourge hits full stride! Featuring the astounding artwork of series artist Eric Battle, and colors by David Curiel, The Scourge #4 is set to infect the comic book community like never before!
name: Tunnel of Hell

description: All participants who survived the Dragon Island tournament are being killed or suffer attacks. Nathan is the last , but for him a more refined plot has been set. Behind it there is Athos Than, the Lord of Dragon Island: to take his revenge, he organized a new tournament where Nathan will have to fight hard for his life, and more ...
name: La vendetta del drago

description: Nathan is brought upon Dragon Star , the space station where Than has his base . The hero must overcome five levels of combat , the death penalty by Li Xiaolong , sensei of the Shaolin temple where Nathan had studied martial arts and that Than has kidnapped . Not only the lives of the antagonists but the very survival of the Shaolin tradition are at stake.
name: Il torneo finale

description: Special POINT ONE Issue. HELL'S OWN ANGEL RETURNS IN ALL NEW POINT ISSUE THAT LEADS STRAIGHT TO THE NEW GHOST RIDER ONGOING SERIES! With the events of FEAR ITSELF tearing the Earth apart a mysterious and powerful figure offers Blaze a faustian pact and a chance for peace. Can Blaze actually allow himself to 'Give Up The Ghost'? And, if so, who will the Ghost Rider pass onto next? The souls of Johnny Blaze and everyone within the Marvel Universe depend on this decision. Vengeance rides in a new direction with Rob Williams (Throwbacks, Daken) and Matthew Clark (Superman, Doom Patrol). Grab your leather, metal and hellfire because it's the end of an era for Ghost Rider and the beginning of a new life for Johnny Blaze. It's gonna get loud! FIRE!
name: Give Up The Ghost

description: Rock was just a simple helper-robot. Now he's the world-saving Mega Man! Armed with only his Mega Buster, can Mega Man face down the Robot Masters? More importantly, can he face his own reservations about fighting his own kind?
name: Let the Games Begin!, Part Two: Weapons Get!

description: The one true Dark Phoenix returns to the Marvel U with a vengeance! As the earth is destroyed, Iron Man is swept into the time-stream where the only chance for survival is to gather the greatest heroes from across the eras and change the course of history! The Avengers, Fantastic Four, the X-Men and more will join Iron Man for this trip through all the ages of Marvel! Rising stars Rob Williams (DARK WOLVERINE) and Rebekah Issacs (MS. MARVEL) team up for the century-spanning epic that takes you through the Marvel Universe’s greatest moments…and maybe to its last!
name: The Iron Age: Alpha

description: The mysterious Catcher has always walked his own path, but for him, time is running out. As another searing story comes to an end, will Catcher finally run out of places to hide?
name: You Gotta Sin to Get Saved, Conclusion: Ain't No God

story_arc_credits.name: You Gotta Sin to Get Saved

first_appearance_storyarcs.name: You Gotta Sin to Get Saved

description: In this new collection featuring issues #12-17, Gus and the other hybrid kids meet a new ally in the militia camp, but will he help them find a way out? And Jepperd begins to assemble an army of his own to take down the militia camp. But can he control the forces he's set in motion? It's the most explosive SWEET TOOTH epic yet!
name: Vol. 3

description: The hammer goes down, the auction starts, and lot number 100 is Tom Taylor. Who's going to be bidding, and what do they want him for? Tom hopes he never finds out - but he's out of options, in the hands of his enemies, and locked in a sensory deprivation tank that's terrifyingly familiar...
name: Citizen Taylor, Part Two of Two

description: Arachne: the man and the spider living in the same body ... Is this the secret that the village of Llandlow  hides so jealously? Its inhabitants, in fact, seem horrible predators hidden in human guise... Looking for Julius Bord, Dylan Dog runs into old legends and dark rituals. Little by little, the fog lifts, but every step in the truth is a thread of spider traps. And for the Investigator there is no escape. Because is he the chosen one ...
name: La profezia

description: There is a world in space where it is impossible to conceal their thoughts. It is a world without surprises, without risk, without interest. And it's for this reason that their inhabitants have come to earth to try out some emotion, and will be very difficult for Dylan to convince them to return to their planet.
name: Incontri ravvicinati

description: A psychologist, using special ESP powers, manages to separate people from their evil part, but unfortunately this leads to suicide crisis or turns people into killers. Only Dylan Dog will be able to resist and defeat his dark half.
name: La metà oscura

description:
A bottle of whiskey that can free the demons, a former homeless man who suddenly disappears and becomes a great writer, a gang of tramps who hires Dylan Dog to exonerate their friend.

All this will happen to Dylan Dog in a quiet (extra-) ordinary spring day.
name: La prigione di carta

description: A fairy tale with his princess, the knight and the inevitable monster. But sometimes reality and fantasy merge and it may happen that the fairy tale characters get mixed up with reality. So what better rider can help the beautiful princess, but Dylan Dog?
name: L'antro della belva

description: A sleep researcher named Joel Dipslip, after undergoing some tests, is no longer able to fall asleep. He begins to confuse reality and fantasy, also assisted by a hellish computer , nightmares, and fears that materialize themselves. Dylan will have to travel again to the Golconda mines, where he meets an old friend.
name: La quinta stagione
